  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803220/extras/ec76fdae9f1de0836139b4b94b89f576.avif?t=1742392628\" width=600 height=215 /></span><br><br>In Koala Kids Golf <strong>you </strong>are the ball! ʕ•ᴥ•ʔ<br>Collect treasure before your opponents. Watch out for traps and dangers or you'll lose your gems!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multi Player</h2>Compete with <strong>Friends!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single Player</h2>..or play <strong>Challenges </strong>to unlock Stars and Customizables.<br>There are also <strong>Platinum Star Achievements</strong> that will truly test your Golfing skills!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Up to 4 Players Local or Online</strong><br></li><li><strong>Challenges!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Handcrafted Levels</strong><br></li><li><strong>Loads of Customization</strong><br></li><li><strong>Cozy Soundtrack!</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Types:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Score Attack: </strong>Get as much score as possible in 8 turns<br></li><li><strong>One Shot Wonder: </strong>Only got one shot!<br></li><li><strong>Combo Wombo: </strong>String together the sickest Combo<br></li><li><strong>Boost Run: </strong>Never stop that momentum</li></ul><br>Can you become the very best aerodynamic Koala? See you out in the fields smoothbrain! ʕ•ᴥ•ʔ ♡<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803220/extras/7a919533d0d663d3015084ba110c80b6.avif?t=1742392628\" width=600 height=228 /></span>",
